::Zeus/Annihilator/Killer::

Zeus fumbles as he catches the grenade, his eyes going wide. He squeezes it 
in his hands to reduce the explosion. The grenade explodes, sending Zeus 
flying through a wall and falling in stasis lock.

Killer walks over to him, picking him up and heading toward the CR chambers, 
grabbing Annihilator on the way.

Having put both of them in CR chambers, he returns to the bridge, sending a 
transmission to Shuko: "Shuko, Megatron, Ra, and anothe' bot have attacked 
th' ship. Ra has betrayed us. We beat them back, and I'm fixin' th' damage."

With that, Killer goes to work on repairing the computer systems that Ra had 
damaged.
